item.title: Chicken Afritada
item.description: Easy to make one-pot chicken dish with vegetables. You can make a large batch and save some for your baon to work. It is a complete ulam where you have the sarsa for the rice and the main deal - chicken and vegetable. Ingredients Chicken Potatoes Carrots Red bell pepper Green bell pepper Tomatoes Garlic Onions Olive oil or canola Tomato sauce Patis (fish sauce) Salt and black pepper to taste Cut into bite-size pieces Procedure Cut the chicken in medium portions.
